The '''Ida'an''' (also '''Idahan''') language is a [[Malayo-Polynesian languages|Malayo-Polynesian]] language spoken by the [[Ida'an]] people of [[Sabah]], [[Malaysia]].

Begak is threatened with [[language death|extinction]], as younger speakers are switching to [[Malay language|Malay]].
